Certainly, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "sredstva" in different forms and positions:

1. *Sredstva* za čišćenje mogu biti veoma korisna u domaćinstvu. (Means "Cleaning agents can be very useful in households.")
2. Ova kompanija ima dovoljno *sredstava* za pokretanje nove kampanje. (Means "This company has enough resources to launch a new campaign.")
3. Naša organizacija se trudi da obezbedi što više *sredstava* za pomoć ugroženim zajednicama. (Means "Our organization is striving to provide as many resources as possible to help vulnerable communities.")
4. *Sredstva* koja su nam na raspolaganju nisu dovoljna za pokrivanje svih troškova. (Means "The resources available to us are not sufficient to cover all costs.")
5. Ministarstvo je izdvojilo dodatna *sredstva* za unapređenje zdravstvenog sistema. (Means "The Ministry has allocated additional funds for the improvement of the healthcare system.")
6. Da bismo rešili ovaj problem, moramo pronaći nova *sredstva* finansiranja. (Means "To solve this problem, we need to find new funding sources.")

